{
  "stem": "1061.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "This was to wear you out, to beat you down, to exhaust you so that they wouldn't even have to burn you anymore because you will do it two yourself, so to say.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Did you work besides-- after that?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, this is only the first phase.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The quarantine was about a month.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we arrived, I'd say, at the end of July, early August-- so probably all of August, we were in so-called quarantine.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then by September, we were sent to cut marshes.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There were some escapees by then from Auschwitz-- not that we knew it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I know now why we were assigned to cut the marshes.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The reason was that apparently the Germans did not want marsh land around the camp for-- because these people who were running-- might want to run away-- would hide there.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we-- we were sent onto this job to cut marshes.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We stood in water.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] It was incredible.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The food-- the-- the food that was given out in-- first of all, you know, in Auschwitz, you had to be out, counted-- you-- roll call, every morning.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "If they didn't like-- if somebody was missing, you could stand there for two hours.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "If they didn't like the way you lined up, you were beaten.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They had-- they gave us what was called coffee, which was water-- which was nothing-- with a little piece of bread that was for the day.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was to last you the day.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You had to line up, to leave through the gate that says, [SPEAKING GERMAN], you know, 'Work makes you free.' Cut marsh in the marshes.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We would walk.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We would-- I don't really know how far, but it had to be a distance, a few miles.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there were these private homes along the way, and people were living lives in those homes.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There were geranium boxes in the window.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There with pillows being aired.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Who these people were who lived there, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Could be the attendant, the Auschwitz attendant, the German attendants with their families or could be-- I don't know who.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But those were homes as we knew homes to be.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we were so far away from anything that could even be called human.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And you know, that-- you think in pictures.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That picture of walking by the homes with the pillows in the windows and the geraniums and such, going to the marshes, standing there in water cutting the-- in the marshes, then coming back to be beaten and line up again.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And if anybody didn't line up, you-- they could keep you there forever.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then going to sleep inside the barracks, nine people to a-- you know, they had bunks.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "One bunk had nine women.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we would sleep head to foot because nine the same way, the same direction, would not fit.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So you had to-- to sleep one way, one this way.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the humiliations-- the daily humiliations of the people who were running the barracks.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I once remembered-- this was also a Czech woman.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Her name was Aranka.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I don't know-- or Slovak.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But they were-- she was one of these hefty, big women.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And one day, I was passing by, she grabbed me by the head.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "She put her foot out on this chair-- she wore leather boots-- and told me to shine with my spit to shine her shoes.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I'm standing there shivering, you know, because I was alone, and I don't know how she got hold of me.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think I was on the-- on the way outside.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was a latrine in the back.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I think I was on the way to the latrine.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Anyhow, I was afraid if I don't do it, she herself could kill me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I mean, with one blow.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know, one blow on the head from her, it would have done it too.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And those-- and even though there was-- we were by now so totally below a level of any humanity, it really-- it really bothered me, you know, this thing.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I mean, why should I be bothered about the fact that she told me to clean her boots by spitting on it then shining when I was going through all of this-- the deprivation, and the hunger, and the lice, and the hard work, and not knowing about my father, and being completely at the mercy of God knows what?",
      "word_count": 60
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Why to-- why be humiliated by that?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I never forgot it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was the utmost-- I still don't know-- you know, I can't put it in-- in a perspective to analyze.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Why would that have bothered me so much?",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
